#~ msgid ""
#~ "\n"
#~ "Now let's have a closer look at the main square.\n"
#~ "\n"
#~ "In the 'Account' tab you get a balance sheet of this island, featuring "
#~ "all costs you pay and all taxes you earn.\n"
